sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Initialization
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over InitContainer,KFPServer: Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Initialization
        participant InitContainer as odh-pipelines-components<br/>(Init Container)
        participant SharedVol as Shared Volume<br/>/config/managed-pipelines
        participant KFPServer as KFP API Server

        InitContainer->>SharedVol: Copy compiled pipeline YAMLs<br/>from /app (Filesystem)
        KFPServer->>SharedVol: Read managed pipeline definitions<br/>(Filesystem mount)
    end

    %% Flow 2: LoRA Fine-Tuning Pipeline
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over DatasetDL,ModelRegAPI: Flow 2: LoRA Fine-Tuning Pipeline
        participant DatasetDL as dataset_download<br/>Component
        participant S3 as S3 / HuggingFace<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant PVC as PVC Workspace<br/>(Shared Storage)
        participant TrainModel as train_model (LoRA)<br/>Component
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Evaluator as universal_llm_evaluator<br/>Component
        participant ArtifactStore as KFP Artifact Store
        participant ModelRegComp as kubeflow_model_registry<br/>Component
        participant ModelRegAPI as Model Registry API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

        DatasetDL->>S3: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / HF Token
        S3-->>DatasetDL: Dataset artifacts
        DatasetDL->>PVC: Write dataset to workspace<br/>(Filesystem)
        TrainModel->>K8sAPI: Create TrainingJob CRD<br/>HTTPS/6443 mTLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>TrainModel: Training status
        Note over TrainModel,PVC: Training pod writes model output to PVC
        Evaluator->>PVC: Read trained model<br/>(Filesystem)
        Evaluator->>ArtifactStore: Write evaluation metrics<br/>(Filesystem)
        ModelRegComp->>ModelRegAPI: Register model with provenance<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext<br/>No auth (in-cluster)
    end

    %% Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over DocsDisc,ArtifactStore2: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
        participant DocsDisc as documents_discovery<br/>Component
        participant S3Rag as S3 Bucket<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant TextExtr as text_extraction<br/>Component
        participant Docling as Docling<br/>(In-process)
        participant SearchPrep as search_space_preparation<br/>Component
        participant OGXAPI as OGX API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant RAGOpt as rag_templates_optimization<br/>Component
        participant LeaderEval as leaderboard_evaluation<br/>Component
        participant ArtifactStore2 as KFP Artifact Store

        DocsDisc->>S3Rag: Discover documents<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM
        S3Rag-->>DocsDisc: Document listing
        TextExtr->>S3Rag: Download documents<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM
        S3Rag-->>TextExtr: Document files
        TextExtr->>Docling: Extract text<br/>(In-process, local)
        Docling-->>TextExtr: Extracted text
        SearchPrep->>OGXAPI: Prepare search space<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API key
        OGXAPI-->>SearchPrep: Search configuration
        RAGOpt->>OGXAPI: Vector store + embeddings<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API key
        OGXAPI-->>RAGOpt: Optimization results
        LeaderEval->>ArtifactStore2: Write evaluation results<br/>(Filesystem)
    end
